review_title: Bright and love the thin bezles
reviews: Compared to other monitors in the market this definitely looks a lot nicer with the thinner bezels, the 450nit brightness guarantees good visibility even under direct sunlight, excellent!
Great product,It works great. Easy to use

The package arrived quickly to my home, well protected and contained the stands, softboxes and light heads. Assembly was easy without any use of my DIY kit needed. The stands feel very strong and the two-tone lighting is very effective depending on the color temperature sought. The light can be set very bright or adjusted to a low, dim setting. Recommend 100%
